    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This performance-oriented example features a high-revving, naturally aspirated flat-six engine mated to a crisp six-speed manual transaxle. The chassis architecture, featuring a sophisticated multi-link rear setup and a mechanical limited-slip differential, remains tight and communicative. The powertrain exhibits excellent thermal management and consistent compression across all cylinders, delivering a linear torque curve through the entire RPM range. Recent maintenance includes a full fluid service and an inspection of the dual-mass flywheel and clutch assembly. While it shows the honest patina of a driven machine, its mechanical integrity is unquestionable, offering a raw, analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
